##Raspberry pi home automation project
Author  : ryanoberto
Description : Raspberry Pi home automation system built in Python there is a client service and a master service, you can use the client service independently

Required Modules:

* APScheduler
* beautifulsoup
* python-pywapi
* PyYAML
* setuptools
* websocket-client
* wiringPi
* flask
* flask-httpauth
* flask_cors
* flask-sqlalchemy
* bootstrap-toggle


Master Dependancies:

* espeak
* python-espeak
* sqlite3
* Flask-WTF

node.py start the node on port 5000 and starts the webserver for you to manage the device independantly
homevolution.py managers the nodes, schedules integrates with kodi, zoneminder. 

Usage:

python node.py	starts the node on port 5000
python homevolution.py starts the master on port 80

Installation Guide:

Client is intended to run on a raspberry pi.

On a default raspbian install:

* apt-get install git python  python-rpi.gpio python-pip  python-yaml python-flask
* pip install python-yaml flask-cors flask.ext.httpauth Flask-HTTPAuth
* python ./node.py

